<h1 style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 30px; border-bottom: 2px solid #000000; padding-bottom: 10px;">
  Message Received
</h1>

<p>Hello <%= @web_form.name %>,</p>

<p>Thank you for reaching out. We have received your inquiry and our team is currently reviewing the details of your project idea.</p>

<p>We will contact you shortly regarding your preferred date: <strong><%= @web_form.contact_date.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></strong>.</p>

<div style="margin: 40px 0; border-top: 1px solid #EEE; padding-top: 20px;">
  <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #666;">Best regards,<br>The Project Team</p>
</div>